hadithonline\/2012\/02\/21\/break-peace-treaty-no-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19142,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Covenants: Whoever betrays peace treaty not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever kills a person protected by a treaty without a just cause, Allah has forbidden Paradise for him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2760 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40808,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/08\/17\/satisfaction-islam-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19142,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Contentment: I am pleased with Allah as Lord","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says, \u2018I am pleased with Allah as a Lord, with Islam as a religion, and with Muhammad as a messenger,\u2019 he must be given Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1529 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0